reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I was looking for
reviews.reviewText: Good quality, very easy to put on (the tiny air hole really does make a difference). It fits tightly without being ridiculously/inconveniently tight. Most impotently, it still fits in my cup holder. I think this is one of the thinner boots I’ve seen. I’ve seen other ones that friends have ordered for their own Stanley & they’re much thicker. So I appreciate how thin this one is without sacrificing protection. Now I don’t have to worry about scratching the bottom of my Stanley in my cup holder/rough surfaces & it’s a lot more quiet when I place it back down on my desk. My only regret is that I didn’t buy this & place it on my Matte 40oz Stanley Quencher when I first bought it because the matte coating is already starting to peel on the bottom. Maybe I’ll older another Matte Stanley & place this one from the start to see if that makes a difference!
